test_source_code:
def test_run_nesting() -> None:
    async def inception() -> None:
        async def main() -> None:  # pragma: no cover
            pass

        return _core.run(main)

    with pytest.raises(RuntimeError) as excinfo:
        _core.run(inception)
    assert "from inside" in str(excinfo.value)
